metadata.name: NOT NASA #1
metadata.description: Unfungible flying objects are NOT NASA, a community-run creative studio which enables creativites and consumers alike to shape the art we interact with and freely inovate. 1,111 unique tokens on the Ethereum-based blockchain will serve as membership - which grant access to creative contribution and shared ownership of NOT NASA Ecosystem Products and Innovations. Also serves as ticket to not Nasa events, merch, art. Love wins ❤️
